===Noun===
'''defibrillator'''
#{{medicine}} An electronic device used [[internally]] or [[externally]] to correct [[ventricular]] [[fibrillation]], a lack of [[coordination]] of the [[contraction]] of muscle tissue of the large chambers of the heart.

